(145, 'Tuyển Dụng Quản Lý Dự Án Doanh Nghiệp - Công Ty CP Vinpearl', 'tuyen-dung-quan-ly-du-an-doanh-nghiep-cong-ty-cp-vinpearl', 'chi-phi-hoc-tap-du-hoc-singapore-gia-re.jpg', 'Tuyển dụng QUẢN LÝ DỰ ÁN DOANH NGHIỆP.\r\nQuản lý dự án tiềm năng, tổ chức quản lý hiệu quả các dự án của doanh nghiệp, ưu tiên người có chứng chỉ PMP.', '', '<h1><strong>QUẢN LÝ DỰ ÁN DOANH NGHIỆP - Project Management</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Tên công ty&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Công Ty Cổ Phần Vinpearl</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website công ty&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; www.vinpearl.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Số nhân viên&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1,000-4,999</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tên liên hệ&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Phòng Hành Chính - Nhân Sự</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in the very first year of the 21st Century, choosing the primitive and poor Hon Tre Island to invest into – that might be a risk for other companies, but it is a brilliant deep-thinking investment of Vinpearl. After approximately 10 years of building and developing, with its appropriate orientation and a thirst for pioneering, Vinpearl has overcome all difficulties and challenges to affirm its capability, becoming internationally renowned for tourism, resort and recreation services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vinpearl now has been widely known by both domestic and foreign tourists for its chain of premium products and services, including: Vinpearl&nbsp; Resort Nha Trang, Vinpearl Resort Phu Quoc, Vinpearl&nbsp; Luxury Nha Trang, Vinpearl Luxury Da Nang, Vinpearl Golf Club Nha Trang, Vinpearl Golf Club Phu Quoc</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the future, the Company plans to make further purposeful and effective investments into tourism infrastructure, real estate and transporting conveyance, with the immediate priority on the chain of luxury resort projects like Vinpearl Quy Nhon, Vinpearl Hoi An, Vinpearl Hanoi etc. Vinpearl is striving to become a tourism and resort brand name of international stature, becoming the lead of Vietnam’s Tourism.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>MÔ TẢ CHI TIẾT CÔNG VIỆC</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Responsible for finding, hunting, searching, interviewing, recruiting for all vacancies of the company</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Take care for position descriptions, job posting, advertising, and applicant communication</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Initiates contact with potential candidates to conduct initial screening and schedule interviews accordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Reviews applications and interviews applicants to obtain work history, education, training, job skills, and salary requirements, and to provide information about the organization and position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Establish and build relationships with other recruitment channels to expand the candidate resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Constantly expanding and reinforcing the candidate resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Organize events, recruiting conference programs, and career fair according to the department’s plans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Dealing with candidates about the salary and benefit based on company policy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Coordinates and makes necessary travel arrangements for candidates who are interviewing or relocating as required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Prepares offer letters of employment for prospective candidates utilizing the Compensation Guidelines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>KINH NGHIỆM/KỸ NĂNG CHI TIẾT</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Good communication in English (Speaking &amp; listening)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Bachelor''s Degree or equivalent education and training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- At least 3-4 years experience recruiting role, preferred in hospitality in</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Interpersonal skill</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ability to work under high pressure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Good presentation, negotiation and problem solving skills</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ability to use discretion when handling sensitive and confidential issues required</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Good communication skills and ability to expand relationships.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>THÔNG TIN LIÊN HỆ</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cách liên hệ:Nộp trực tuyến, Gửi kèm File, Trực tiếp</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mô tả:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Please send your application by online, email or direct to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tên liên hệ:Phòng Hành Chính - Nhân Sự</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Địa chỉ:Đảo Hòn Tre, Vĩnh Nguyên, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa, Việt Nam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguời liên hệ:Ms Hà Uyên</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhận hồ sơ ứng viên bằng ngôn ngữ: Tiếng Anh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngày gởi: 03/11/2014&nbsp;&nbsp; Ngày hết hạn: 03/12/2014</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguồn xem chi tiết &amp; đăng ký : <a href="http://www.careerlink.vn/tim-viec-lam/recruitement-executive/591509?keywords=pmp&amp;s=0"><span style="color:#FF0000;">Tại Đây</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<div style="border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center; background: rgb(238, 238, 238);">Mời các bạn xem thêm những việc làm liên quan <a href="http://stevbros.edu.vn/hot-job-quan-ly-du-an-pmp"><span style="color:#FF0000;">Tại Đây</span></a></div>\r\n\r\n<h2><em><q>Stevbros đang cung cấp khóa học qua mạng cho các chuyên gia quản lý dự án ở 106 quốc gia trên thế giới và đào tạo chuyên gia quản lý dự án cho các doanh nghiệp và cá nhân trong khu vực châu Á.</q></em></h2>\r\n', '2014-11-14 17:40:28', '2014-11-14 18:02:18', 1, 'tuyển dụng quản lý dự án, hot job pmp, việc làm quản lý dự án, dự án phần mềm, quản lý dự án CNTT, việc làm pmp', 0, 0, NULL, ',367,', '', '', '', 'bao', 'bao', 0),
