(112, 'Phạm Nhất Phương, Training Director at FPT Software', 'pham-nhat-phuong-training-director-at-fpt-software', '', 'Our experience to date with the professionals from Stevbros has been excellent! They have worked with us to create wonderful programs for our most important asset, our people. We highly appreciate their supports and we would like to have further partnership with Stevbros in long-term.', '', '<div><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">“FSOFT Corporate Training Center has partnered with Stevbros in Scrum for Developer programs in order to enhance our developers’ skills and expertise in Scum projects. Our experience to date with the professionals from Stevbros has been excellent! They have worked with us to create wonderful programs for our most important asset, our people. We highly appreciate their supports and care. </span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">We celebrated our graduating class and the success of the program has been measured by the placement of a majority of our graduates in management positions. As receiving positive feedbacks from our own employees who attended these training programs, we would like to have further partnership with Stevbros in long-term. We look forward to the career success of future graduates and our partnership with Stevbros."</span></div>\r\n', '2014-08-02 10:04:45', '2014-08-08 11:45:44', 1, '', 0, 0, NULL, ',31,', '', '', '', 'admin', 'admin', 0),
